videos.description: LeBron James and Anthony Davis thank Lakers fans for their support as they raise their 17th championship banner at Staples Center before their game against the Rockets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lakers raise 17th championship banner after LeBron, AD thank fans) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lakers raise 17th championship banner after LeBron, AD thank fans

videos.description: Cameron Oliver gets the pass and elevates to throw down a stylish 360 dunk under the basket that no one expected.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Cameron Oliver throws down surprising 360 dunk under the basket) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cameron Oliver throws down surprising 360 dunk under the basket

videos.description: Talen Horton-Tucker finds Montrezl Harrell for a dunk in transition and LeBron celebrates as he gets up off the bench to flex along the baseline.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron hyped on the sideline after Lakers capitalize on the break) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron hyped on the sideline after Lakers capitalize on the break

videos.description: Kyle Kuzma slips a dime behind his back to a streaking Montrezl Harrell for an emphatic slam in the paint.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kuzma goes behind-the-back to Harrell for the slam) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kuzma goes behind-the-back to Harrell for the slam

videos.description: Talen Horton-Tucker beats his defender off the dribble and flies to the basket to hammer down a vicious one-handed slam in the middle of the lane.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (THT soars to the rack for devastating throwdown) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: THT soars to the rack for devastating throwdown

videos.description: Kenyon Martin Jr. saves the Rockets on defense as he elevates to completely shut down the easy dunk attempt by Devontae Cacok in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (K-Mart Jr. says no to Cacok's dunk attempt) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: K-Mart Jr. says no to Cacok's dunk attempt

videos.description: Kyle Kuzma uses a Eurostep to make a tough go-ahead layup as the Lakers pull out a 124-122 win over the Rockets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kuzma hits clutch layup in closing moments vs. Rockets) 2021/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kuzma hits clutch layup in closing moments vs. Rockets
